data.description:
This charming tri-level home, situated on a spacious 0.42-acre lot in a serene neighborhood boasts 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1969 square feet of living space.

Inside this house you will discover a newly remodeled main bathroom, all new Frigidaire appliances in the kitchen, new carpeting in the den and updated paint throughout.

Beyond the interior, the 0.42-acre lot offers ample outdoor space. Enjoy your spacious back deck and private yard, watching wildlife, gardening, and creating your own outdoor oasis. 

Located in a tranquil neighborhood, this home combines modern updates with generous living spaces, offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting tri-level property your new home.
